@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Obtener todos los pagos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tuition-payments

###

### Obtener pago por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tuition-payments/1

###

### Crear pago
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tuition-payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enrollment_id": 1,
  "reference": "REF123456789",
  "method": "Efectivo",
  "amount": 952000,
  "payment_date": "2025-02-01",
  "due_date": "2025-03-01",
  "period_month": 2,
  "period_year": 2025,
  "status": "paid"
}

###

### Actualizar pago
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tuition-payments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "paid",
  "method": "Transferencia"
}

###

### Eliminar pago fisicamente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tuition-payments/1

###

### Eliminar pago logicamente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tuition-payments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "cancelled"
}
